item.title: Spider-Man on PC! I Am Groot! Trick or Read!
item.description: Spider-Man swings into the pages of Spider-Man’s Social Dilemma and the screens of Marvel’s Spider-Man Remastered for PC! Baby Groot dances onto the Disney+ screen! Plus, Ryan and Lorraine talk about some behind the scenes scoops from Marvel Studios’ Thor: Love and Thunder and Ms. Marvel. And we find out which Spider-Man stories you love the most! item.title: NRL 360 - Ponga & Mann drug tested by the NRL & the Knights are lacking leadership - 16/08/22
item.description:
Catch up on all the Rugby League news from NRL360, Tuesday the 16th of August, with host Braith Anasta and of course, Paul Kent.

The duo are joined by Paul Crawley and Dave Riccio to dissect the news that Kalyn Ponga and Kurt Mann have been drug tested by the NRL following their toilet cubicle incident, before turning their attention to the Manly players who flashed gang signs just weeks after the pride jersey saga...
